Insightly: Enhanced Google Search with AI Insights

Make your Google searches smarter with Insightly! This extension seamlessly integrates with your regular Google search, bringing the power of OpenAI's ChatGPT directly to your search results. As you search, Insightly provides additional insights, suggestions, or deeper explanations about your query, displayed elegantly on the right side of your search results.

Features:

AI-Powered Insights: Leverage the intelligence of ChatGPT to get more from your Google searches.
Seamless Integration: No extra clicks or new tabs. Insightly works directly within your regular Google search interface.
Elegant Design: AI insights presented in a readable format, designed to complement your search experience without cluttering it.
Safe & Secure: Insightly respects your privacy. Your search queries are only used to fetch insights and are not stored or used for any other purposes.
Upgrade your search experience with Insightly, and discover the web with the power of AI at your fingertips!
